      *<ORDER SHEET>
     C                     MOVE ' '       @FIRST  1
     C                     MOVEL'1'       *INOF
     C                     Z-ADD0         IHTOTL
     C*
     C                     EXCPTDT0
     C*--------------------
     C*--------------------
S1   C                     DO   *HIVAL
